WEBVTT

00:12:28.769 --> 00:12:31.427
So this is their conception
of a life well lived.

00:12:31.799 --> 00:12:34.103
And people look at this, in the West,

00:12:34.127 --> 00:12:36.826
and well-educated, over-educated,

00:12:36.850 --> 00:12:38.302
people with PhDs

00:12:38.326 --> 00:12:41.485
and people who have
careers as bioethicists,

00:12:41.509 --> 00:12:47.143
people for whom thinking
about what is good and right and beautiful

00:12:47.167 --> 00:12:49.778
in a Western context, that is their job,

00:12:49.802 --> 00:12:51.636
they look at this diversity of opinion

00:12:51.660 --> 00:12:55.470
and they say, "Well, who are we
to say that this is wrong?

00:12:55.494 --> 00:12:58.818
All we can say is that we don't want
to live that way,

00:12:58.842 --> 00:13:00.397
but it's mere preference."